column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: STIMOROL FUSION GUM PEPPERMINT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 05034660521273
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (maltitol, sorbitol, maltitol syrup, sorbitol syrup, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, flavourings, humectant (E422), gelatine, colours (E171, E133), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), glazing agent (E903), thickener (E466). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine.. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
